00:02:12.980 --> 00:02:18.080
After several minutes, he had succeeded at coaxing the elephant inside the box.

00:02:18.740 --> 00:02:23.310
The man slammed the door behind him, and a group of 30

00:02:23.320 --> 00:02:27.840
strong men spun the box around, turning it on itself.

00:02:29.250 --> 00:02:32.670
Several minutes went by, and then the door was opened.

00:02:33.940 --> 00:02:36.410
The anxious audience looked inside.

00:02:37.470 --> 00:02:41.760
The elephant was gone, it had vanished into thin air.

